{"type": "article", "id": 63147, "title": "Ports 1961 创意总监离职，以及，西太后与 ASICS 联名鞋款发布| 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2019-04-22T09:01:05Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 12642, "name": "ASICS"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 574557, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 18, "image": "img/article/article_show/201904221013408rpXHBidKMvQbDcI.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><strong><a href=\"https://us.fashionnetwork.com/news/Schiaparelli-and-Bertrand-Guyon-part-ways,1091248.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">Schiaparelli 创意总监 Bertrand Guyon 离职</a>&nbsp;</strong>|&nbsp;Bertrand Guyon 曾于 Valentino 就职，后于 2015 年加入 Schiaparelli 担任创意总监，据媒体报道在任期间品牌业绩令人满意。 Schiaparelli 于 2006 年被意大利集团 Tod's CEO Diego Della Valle 收购，将于今年 5 月 8 日迎来品牌成立 350 周年。在上周四发布的声明中，品牌方简单感谢了创意总监，但并未对其离职原因及继任者做出任何解释。</p><p><strong><a href=\"https://wwd.com/fashion-news/designer-luxury/natasa-cagalj-exits-ports-1203113481/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ports 1961 创意总监&nbsp;</a><a href=\"https://wwd.com/fashion-news/designer-luxury/ports-1961-taps-cagalj-for-creative-post-8077331/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nataša Čagalj</a><a href=\"https://wwd.com/fashion-news/designer-luxury/natasa-cagalj-exits-ports-1203113481/\" rel=\"nofollow\">&nbsp;离职</a>&nbsp;</strong>|&nbsp;Nataša Čagalj&nbsp;于 2014 年加入 Ports 1961 任创意总监，此前还曾先后在 Nino Cerruti、Peter Speliopoulos、Lanvin、Stella McCartney 任职。她负责的最后一个系列于今年 2 月的伦敦时装周发布。Ports 由加拿大企业家 Luke Tanabe 创立于 1961 年，5 年后被更名为 Ports International，随后更换过两任创意总监。2004 年新任创意总监 Fiona 和 Tia Cibani 姐妹将其更名为 Ports 1961，并将总部从纽约先后搬至米兰以及如今的伦敦。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><strong><a href=\"https://hypebeast.com/2019/4/vivienne-westwood-asics-collection-gel-kayano-5-og-mai-knit-details\" rel=\"nofollow\">Vivienne Westwood&nbsp;与&nbsp;ASICS 发布首波联名系列。</a></strong><br></p><p>发布的两个鞋款分别以 GEL-KAYANO 5 OG 以及 GEL-MAL KNIT 为基础。印花灵感来自 Vivienne Westwood 1981 秋冬系列中出现过的“Squiggle”印花（波形曲线）。新鞋款将于 4 月 27 日在 Vivienne Westwood 和 ASICS 网站上发售，分别售价 180 和 190 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190422094428pcImZ24BbDRoNvdy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500586\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190422094429KXCNTmwP75MhpQEY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500586\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190422094428rchbalzIsSt8jCX2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500586\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190422094429F2xQu7r6tnmRsYyf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500586\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190422094429ng9xwFQyLRAcbIvz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500586\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190422094430eDUAcE9qHobp5xZS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500586\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190422094435tvs4uXWCrkHPOY5M.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500586\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190422094434Bawp7tiuUAfjJGcs.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500586\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190422094436Y8Si2vaLAH1oIjwF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500586\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190422094435cJCouFEyYi2VOeLK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500586\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201904220944303FT5IrdAkbpEWugw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500586\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190422094434ZyrOn8a9hldzHQTU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500586\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201904220944367hL8EuCP9M53KarN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500586\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190422094437S7HGx0WNIvzeBusw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500586\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://us.fashionnetwork.com/news/Everlane-to-launch-new-eco-friendly-sneaker-label-Tread,1091513.html#.XL0fbJMzbOQ\" rel=\"nofollow\">Everlane 将于 4 月 25 日推出球鞋环保品牌 Tread。</a></strong></p><p>旧金山品牌 Everlane 此前也曾推出女式球鞋，但新品牌 Tread 将是其首次进入男女式鞋履领域。首款中性极简风球鞋 the Trainer 售价 98 美元，据称只是用了 6% 的新塑料成分，由一家获得环保金级评价的皮革厂提供皮料。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190422100838tONJZfUkTyvVpron.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.250769\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>在全球拥有 150 万粉丝的19 岁虚拟网红&nbsp;Lil Miquela（Instagram 账号为&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/lilmiquela/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">@lilmiquela</a>）<strong><a href=\"https://highxtar.com/club-404-lil-miquela-launches-her-own-clothing-line/?lang=en\" rel=\"nofollow\">创立了她的首个时装系列 Club 404</a></strong>。<br></p><p><a href=\"https://club-404.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">该系列</a>以印有迷幻印花的 T 恤和袜子为主，以“Digital Psychedelia”（数字迷幻）为口号，强调流行文化、霓虹色调和复古审美。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190422100509ZvjRS5DAbkeMlx2O.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.249531\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Lil Miquela</figcaption> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190422100653F1XzUY0tWr8nOS4s.png\" data-ratio=\"0.478382\" data-format=\"png\"><figcaption>CLUB 404 官网截图</figcaption> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://fashionfav.com/magazine-editorials/chris-diena-jiaji-jin-mens-uno-china/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><em>MEN’S UNO CHINA </em>2019 年三月刊造型特辑：TOYHOOD。</a></strong><br></p><p>模特：Chris Diena，Levi Overvest，Josef Ptacek，Richards Drevinskis，摄影：Jiaji Jin，造型：Evan Feng。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190422095250HBGlQM8h6L10O7wI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.231250\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190422095250VYhyDAv4J5WPMbXT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.231250\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190422095250IqmiEG45s0Rj3rYl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.231250\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190422095248EDWg85XyIVkstUH7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.231250\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190422095247B64j1bQiVct5OLSF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.231250\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201904220952491YEy3TOsNG40laWv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.231250\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190422095248cedqJuM057Cs8p9E.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.231250\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190422095248e5DVH4MiTt2z3cCd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.231250\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190422095247OZqwMQhWj2R6tBfv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.756250\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>题图来自&nbsp;<a href=\"https://hypebeast.com/2019/4/vivienne-westwood-asics-collection-gel-kayano-5-og-mai-knit-details\" rel=\"nofollow\">Vivienne Westwood X ASICS&nbsp;</a></p>"}